==English==
===Etymology===
From Latin ''[[mortarium]]''.

=== Noun ===
'''mortar'''
#{{uncountable}} A mixture of [[lime]] or [[cement]], [[sand]] and [[water]] used for [[bonding]] [[brick|bricks]] and [[stone|stones]].
#{{countable}} A short large-bore [[cannon]] that fires [[shell|shells]].
#{{countable}} A [[vessel]] used to grind [[ingredient|ingredients]] with a [[pestle]].

